  "texts": [
    "The LLM's capability to generate coherent and contextually appropriate responses makes it a crucial component of the CRC.",
    "• RetrieverThe retriever component is responsible for fetching relevant information from the document based on the user's query.",
    "The model employs the faiss library from langchain_community.vectorstores to create a vector store using the document embeddings generated earlier.",
    "These embeddings transform text chunks into numerical representations that capture their semantic content.",
    "The vector store allows for efficient retrieval of document sections (chunks) that are semantically similar to the user's query."
  ],
